= - \frac{1}{rv} \left( 2\rho v + r\rho \frac{dv}{dr} \right) \tag{9}\]

<p>ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\begin{align}
&amp;v \frac{dv}{dr} 
= \frac{a^2}{\rho} \frac{1}{rv} \left( 2 \rho v + r \rho \frac{dv}{dr}\right) - \frac{GM_r}{r^2} (1-\Gamma_\mathrm{rad}) 
