\[v \frac{dv}{dr} 
= - \frac{1}{\rho} \frac{dP_\mathrm{gas}}{dr} - \frac{GM}{r^2} (1-\Gamma_\mathrm{e} - \Gamma_\kappa) \tag{17}\]

<p>ãŒå¾—ã‚‰ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
